g.text: This diagram shows how to configure the [CLIENT_API_URL/CLIENT_RPC_URL] environment
variables to connect to the frp-panel master via wss/ws/grpc/http/https
Please first look at the diagram to select the port and connection route you want to use, and
configure the client connection information according to the (orange/green) environment variable
If your environment variable configuration is similar to the format of any value shown in orange,
please consider switching to the green configuration link
If your environment variable configuration is similar to the format of any value shown in green,
1. The server/client can access the public network example.com:port
2. The CLIENT_API_URL and CLIENT_RPC_URL environment variables must be configured
